\b0 \cf0 IdentitySample builds a utility which demonstrates how to use the CoreServices Identity API to manage system-wide identities.  These identities can then be used by applications to enable secure collaboration among users on a network.  The utility allows you to add and delete identities, change identity information as well as query for identities by name.\
